729030f-a.text:
431 to 421 (right to left) Jersey Street, east side (houses thereon), at, adjoining and north of the N.E. corner of Scribner Ave. The view is northward on Brighton Ave. which terminates at Jersey Street. Continuing north from Jersey Street is Scribner
Ave.
July 21, 1932.
P.L. Sperr.
